::DarkMouse::

She slowly opened her eyes and looked around.  Her vision was a 
little blurred.  She blinked and cleared her sight.  She was in the 
lab. She could see the walls and the ceiling of the lab. She shivered 
as a cold wave ran over her body. Her face and body felt cold and 
damp.  She had been in a cold sweat while laying on the table.  She 
heard voices in the distance.  She felt scared.  She couldn't move 
and couldn't make out the voices.  She shivered slightly as another 
cold wave swept over her.
